body:
Vegetation & Variations is a texture pack that brings variants to existing vegetation-related blocks in Minecraft!

New textures, along with some older ones, break up the monotony of existing textures in Minecraft. There are also some hidden easter eggs. Hope you can find them!

<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/024lyxmeT7g" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>

Some blocks that have received texture variants include:

Natural blocks:
Grass block;
Short grass;
Dirt;
Dirt path;
Coarse dirt;
Podzol;
Mycelium

Flowers:
Poppy;
Dandelion;
Cornflower;
Blue orchid;
Oxeye daisy;
Azure bluet;
Allium;
Wither rose.

Nether fungi:
Crimson and Warped fungus;
Crimson and Warped nylium;
Nether and Warped wart block;
Crimson and Warped roots.

Others:
Cactus;
Carved pumpkin;
Jack'o'lantern;
Brown and red mushrooms;
Oak, pale oak and jungle leaves

Suggestions and feedbacks are welcome!
Thank you!
